  <Subsection title="Textures">
    <Paragraph>
      An <Term type="term">texture</Term> is a <Link target="71f3233f-43eb-4ea1-96d4-bc1192553239">2D texture</Link>,
      an <Link target="60f44a91-49a1-4ee9-9659-45ed94051828">array texture</Link>, or a
      <Link target="63a0f8cf-4a48-47bc-aa83-b35d631ad243">cube texture</Link>.
    </Paragraph>

    <FormalItem title="Texture">
      <Verbatim><xi:include href="76.txt" parse="text"/></Verbatim>
    </FormalItem>
  </Subsection>

  <Subsection title="2D Texture"
              id="71f3233f-43eb-4ea1-96d4-bc1192553239">
    <Paragraph>
      A 2D texture aggregates <Link target="4ae63d09-ce2d-46d4-a8eb-f1f9ad382ee8">image information</Link> and
      a sequence of <Link target="b8d20538-e4ac-4674-aa43-d5ab93c07149">mipmaps</Link> for a single two-dimensional
      texture.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph id="909468f0-a253-4e8f-82ff-6a6909bf1220">
      2D textures must have <Link target="3dde6403-729d-4eaa-9179-17d9a9fbe7a6">sizeZ</Link> values equal to
      <Term type="constant">1</Term>.
    </Paragraph>
    <FormalItem title="2D Texture">
      <Verbatim><xi:include href="145.txt" parse="text"/></Verbatim>
    </FormalItem>
  </Subsection>

  <Subsection title="Array Texture"
              id="4947de09-7eb6-4439-90e1-1b94adcf8d0a">
    <Paragraph>
      An array texture aggregates <Link target="4ae63d09-ce2d-46d4-a8eb-f1f9ad382ee8">image information</Link> and
      a sequence of <Link target="f4b4fff9-a443-4430-a37b-ed939e606bef">array mipmaps</Link> for a single
      two-dimensional array texture.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph id="e824acd8-5c93-4874-9e17-2010d189bc86">
      Array textures must have <Link target="3dde6403-729d-4eaa-9179-17d9a9fbe7a6">sizeZ</Link> values equal to
      the number of <Link target="cb73941f-ab0c-46cd-a8a2-94ca912eda3a">array layers</Link> in the texture.
    </Paragraph>
    <FormalItem title="Array Texture">
      <Verbatim><xi:include href="146.txt" parse="text"/></Verbatim>
    </FormalItem>
  </Subsection>

  <Subsection title="3D Texture"
              id="60f44a91-49a1-4ee9-9659-45ed94051828">
    <Paragraph>
      3D textures are not yet specified.
    </Paragraph>
  </Subsection>

  <Subsection title="Cube Texture"
              id="63a0f8cf-4a48-47bc-aa83-b35d631ad243">
    <Paragraph>
      A cube texture aggregates <Link target="4ae63d09-ce2d-46d4-a8eb-f1f9ad382ee8">image information</Link> and
      a sequence of <Link target="e8125add-3c83-47a1-9997-1f15867068dd">cube mipmaps</Link> for a single cube
      texture.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph id="21c2587a-17e5-45fb-b17f-968814d2ba17">
      Cube textures must have <Link target="3dde6403-729d-4eaa-9179-17d9a9fbe7a6">sizeZ</Link> values equal to
      <Term type="constant">1</Term>.
    </Paragraph>
    <FormalItem title="Cube Image">
      <Verbatim><xi:include href="154.txt" parse="text"/></Verbatim>
    </FormalItem>
  </Subsection>

</Section>
